# {{component_name}} Troubleshooting

When diagnosing incidents, start with **General Triage** and then refer to the relevant runbook.

## Runbooks

| Runbook | When to use |
|---------|-------------|
| [General Triage](runbooks/triage.md) | First response to any incident — check error rate, search logs, verify dependencies |
| [Common Issues](runbooks/common-issues.md) | Known failure patterns and their resolutions |

## Adding Runbooks

To add a new runbook:
1. Create a markdown file in `skills/troubleshooting/runbooks/`
2. Add a row to the table above
3. Include: symptoms, diagnostic steps (with tool calls), and resolution
